➜航拍内蒙古乌兰淖 色彩斑斓如油画
http://www.sohu.com/a/420541654_162522	19021
<p><span>来源：<span>中新网</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>
<p>2020-09-24 13:12</p>
<p><i><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200924/da93ae47e80c4c03941f2af25f9f2270.jpeg" /></i></p>
<p><i><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200924/7e305a0a288a4d8dbfdb16d4b17cb024.jpeg" /></i></p>
